    RETURN TO TITLE SCREEN</color></size>'
  message100: 'Congratulations!

    You reached <color=#FFD54A>{PERCENT}%</color>
    completion.

    That is only the beginning.

    Can you go beyond 100%, clear
    every stage without using items,

    and unlock the remaining Bombers?'
  message101To199: 'Amazing work!

    You pushed the demo to <color=#FFD54A>{PERCENT}%</color>
    completion.

    You are getting closer to total mastery.

    Keep pushing further,

    clear
    more stages without using items,

    and unlock every Bomber!'
  message200NotAllBombers: 'Incredible!

    You reached the full <color=#FFD54A>{PERCENT}%</color>
    completion.

    Every stage has been perfected.

    Now finish the last challenge:

    unlock
    every Bomber!'
